# EasyTripPlanner 

EasyTripPlanner is a full-stack travel planning website that allows users to plan trips, manage bookings, and complete secure payments.

---

## Features
- User authentication using JWT
- Trip planning with dynamic cost calculation
- Booking management
- Secure payment integration (Cashfree)
- Environment-based configuration (no secrets committed)

---

## ?? Tech Stack

### Frontend
- React.js
- Bootsstrap
- Redux
- REST APIs

### Backend
- ASP.NET Core Web API
- JWT Authentication
- Entity Framework Core
- SQL Server

### Payment Gateway
- Cashfree (Sandbox)

